 </refsect1>
 <refsect1 id="{@id description}">
  <title>Description</title>
  <para>The <emphasis>setIndeterminate()</emphasis> method is used to switch
   the progress abr in indeterminate mode. 
   Read {@tutorial indeterminate.pkg} to learn how to animate a progress bar 
   to show unknown length-task activity.
  </para>
 </refsect1>
